Goal:
Define how a citizen enters the platform using existing
EU-recognized identities without creating parallel identities.

Scope:
- Identity entry (SPID / CIE / eIDAS / EUDI Wallet)
- Proof-of-link only (no identity duplication)
- Consent model (GDPR-min)
- Fail-closed behavior
- Public trust diagram

Non-goals:
- Acting as identity provider
- Storing legal identity data
- Replacing national or EU ID systems

Deliverables:
- Architecture diagram
- Written trust model
- Audit events specification
area:platform
area:identity
type:spec
priority:P0
